  "label": "Sorian Tebb",
  "description": "This individual is a human of middle years, distinguished by bronze skin marked with ingrained work-wear at the knuckles and along the forearms. Brown eyes sit beneath heavy lids and a straight brow ridge, giving the face a steady, appraising cast. Brown hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped style that leaves the ears exposed and the hairline sharply defined. A trimmed beard frames a broad jaw and reinforces an overall impression of durable health and long habituation to hard service.",
